Summary:

The reviewers seem to enjoy the food at Sonny's, especially the burgers and fries. They appreciate that it is a family-owned business that has been around for many years, and they find the food to be fresh and of good quality. Some reviewers mention that the service can be slow, but they feel that the food is worth the wait.

